1
00:00:39,350 --> 00:00:43,730
[Qingchuan's Veil of Vengeance]

2
00:00:45,270 --> 00:00:47,910
[Chu-Xia Border, Chuanhe Inn]

3
00:00:50,240 --> 00:00:51,560
Qi,

4
00:00:53,150 --> 00:00:54,470
how's the situation?

5
00:00:57,200 --> 00:00:59,470
The city's defenders are
fighting desperately.

6
00:00:59,470 --> 00:01:00,790
Many people in Qingchuan Town

7
00:01:00,790 --> 00:01:02,240
refuse to abandon it.

8
00:01:02,470 --> 00:01:04,069
They still trust the Mo Army.

9
00:01:04,069 --> 00:01:04,680
However,

10
00:01:05,120 --> 00:01:06,320
the battle is fierce,

11
00:01:07,150 --> 00:01:09,150
and the Chu forces are unstoppable.

12
00:01:09,430 --> 00:01:10,680
Qingchuan Town

13
00:01:11,990 --> 00:01:13,920
has fallen and the people are dead.

14
00:01:16,270 --> 00:01:19,370
[Summer, the 12th year of the Xia Dynasty]

15
00:01:21,560 --> 00:01:23,760
Though Father has passed,

16
00:01:24,039 --> 00:01:26,570
the Uncles and Commanders
still hold strong.

17
00:01:26,820 --> 00:01:29,420
How could the front lines
collapse so quickly?

18
00:01:30,400 --> 00:01:31,950
Besides, my flanking attack

19
00:01:31,950 --> 00:01:33,660
even ran into elite troops.

20
00:01:34,060 --> 00:01:36,090
How did Chu manage this?

21
00:01:36,840 --> 00:01:39,640
How could Qingchuan Town
possibly have been lost?

22
00:01:40,039 --> 00:01:40,960
This is impossible.

23
00:01:40,960 --> 00:01:42,400
Absolutely impossible.

24
00:01:45,700 --> 00:01:46,729
Mo Qingchuan!

25
00:01:46,840 --> 00:01:48,030
Surrender immediately,

26
00:01:48,030 --> 00:01:49,690
or my army will burn this inn
to the ground!

27
00:01:49,690 --> 00:01:50,250
Sir,

28
00:01:50,280 --> 00:01:52,120
our inn has always been neutral territory.

29
00:01:52,120 --> 00:01:52,759
Get out!

30
00:01:53,150 --> 00:01:54,350
It's Feng Shiye.

31
00:01:54,640 --> 00:01:55,509
Go quickly.

32
00:01:55,509 --> 00:01:56,950
They're after me.

33
00:01:57,710 --> 00:01:58,680
Hurry!

34
00:01:58,680 --> 00:02:00,080
This is a military order!

35
00:02:02,760 --> 00:02:03,640
General!

36
00:02:07,010 --> 00:02:08,630
[Episode 5]

37
00:02:07,010 --> 00:02:08,630
[Qingchuan's Veil of Vengeance]

38
00:02:08,740 --> 00:02:11,550
Episode 5: Execution

39
00:02:15,320 --> 00:02:19,160
[Imperial Prison]

40
00:02:35,190 --> 00:02:39,820
[Qingxin Cottage]

41
00:02:38,960 --> 00:02:40,050
That was too close.

42
00:02:40,190 --> 00:02:42,079
If those old comrades
recognize you by day,

43
00:02:42,079 --> 00:02:43,520
won't your true identity

44
00:02:43,520 --> 00:02:44,610
be exposed?

45
00:02:45,920 --> 00:02:47,430
I've decided to return to the capital.

46
00:02:47,430 --> 00:02:48,590
The identity of Mo Wang

47
00:02:48,590 --> 00:02:49,920
was never meant to last.

48
00:02:51,460 --> 00:02:53,500
It's just a bold disguise

49
00:02:53,630 --> 00:02:54,560
so the world

50
00:02:54,560 --> 00:02:56,570
won't link me to Mo Qingchuan for now.

51
00:02:56,570 --> 00:02:57,910
If it's uncovered,

52
00:02:58,640 --> 00:02:59,710
the one who should panic

53
00:02:59,710 --> 00:03:00,560
isn't me.

54
00:03:02,500 --> 00:03:05,100
Ms. Mo, do you think Qiguang
has figured it out?

55
00:03:07,360 --> 00:03:08,820
He's starting to suspect.

56
00:03:11,690 --> 00:03:13,930
Then why not tell him the truth?

57
00:03:18,100 --> 00:03:19,650
Everyone hates Mo Qingchuan,

58
00:03:19,650 --> 00:03:20,780
except for him.

59
00:03:22,790 --> 00:03:23,920
I remember

60
00:03:23,940 --> 00:03:26,000
the way he looked when he spoke of her.

61
00:03:29,150 --> 00:03:30,430
Her light

62
00:03:30,780 --> 00:03:32,579
still shines on that boy.

63
00:03:34,690 --> 00:03:36,820
And now that I live in darkness,

64
00:03:37,870 --> 00:03:39,070
let me steal his light

65
00:03:39,840 --> 00:03:40,800
a little later—

66
00:03:41,520 --> 00:03:42,870
just a little later.

67
00:03:52,870 --> 00:03:53,680
What if

68
00:03:53,680 --> 00:03:55,520
he believes in both Mo Qingchuan

69
00:03:55,650 --> 00:03:57,090
and Mo Wang?

70
00:04:03,500 --> 00:04:07,020
[Qingxin Cottage]

71
00:04:03,930 --> 00:04:05,560
I'm here to see Master.

72
00:04:06,150 --> 00:04:06,960
Come in.

73
00:04:10,830 --> 00:04:15,720
[Qingxin Cottage]

74
00:04:16,410 --> 00:04:17,380
Come and eat.

75
00:04:34,830 --> 00:04:35,930
Master, you

76
00:04:36,480 --> 00:04:38,740
seem to especially like green plum wine.

77
00:04:39,610 --> 00:04:40,420
Yes.

78
00:04:43,360 --> 00:04:45,120
Qingchuan Town's green plum wine

79
00:04:45,120 --> 00:04:46,580
is famous across the land.

80
00:04:47,320 --> 00:04:48,360
I wonder if you

81
00:04:48,390 --> 00:04:49,520
have ever tasted it?

82
00:04:49,570 --> 00:04:50,409
I have.

83
00:04:50,550 --> 00:04:51,880
I used to drink it often.

84
00:04:52,310 --> 00:04:53,110
Master,

85
00:04:55,159 --> 00:04:56,760
are you from Qingchuan Town?

86
00:04:57,390 --> 00:04:58,190
Yes.

87
00:04:59,360 --> 00:05:00,370
So am I.

88
00:05:05,730 --> 00:05:06,690
Then why

89
00:05:07,490 --> 00:05:09,490
have you never mentioned it before?

90
00:05:11,020 --> 00:05:12,590
It's nothing special.

91
00:05:12,920 --> 00:05:14,920
No need to bring it up deliberately.

92
00:05:19,800 --> 00:05:20,830
Master,

93
00:05:21,300 --> 00:05:22,760
have you met Mo Qingchuan?

94
00:05:24,920 --> 00:05:25,720
Yes, I have.

95
00:05:26,380 --> 00:05:27,910
I'm very familiar with her.

96
00:05:28,920 --> 00:05:29,680
Master,

97
00:05:32,060 --> 00:05:33,260
are you Mo Qingchuan?

98
00:05:37,140 --> 00:05:37,940
No, I'm not.

99
00:05:43,700 --> 00:05:45,560
I knew I couldn't hide it from you.

100
00:05:46,640 --> 00:05:47,350
Actually,

101
00:05:47,380 --> 00:05:48,980
I was once part of the Mo Army.

102
00:05:49,030 --> 00:05:50,360
My codename is Shuicao.

103
00:05:50,870 --> 00:05:52,890
I was General Mo Qingchuan's shadow guard.

104
00:05:52,890 --> 00:05:53,480
That's why

105
00:05:53,480 --> 00:05:55,940
I learned the Mo family's
blade techniques.

106
00:05:56,380 --> 00:05:57,300
Then why...

107
00:05:58,560 --> 00:06:00,040
Why have I never

108
00:06:00,060 --> 00:06:01,160
seen you

109
00:06:01,270 --> 00:06:02,630
use those techniques before?

110
00:06:02,630 --> 00:06:04,690
I was gravely injured during the war.

111
00:06:05,070 --> 00:06:06,930
My inner strength was destroyed.

112
00:06:09,360 --> 00:06:10,190
I

113
00:06:10,800 --> 00:06:12,440
am not Mo Qingchuan.

114
00:06:18,380 --> 00:06:19,600
I understand.

115
00:06:23,600 --> 00:06:24,560
Come, eat.

116
00:06:25,030 --> 00:06:25,800
Alright.

117
00:06:34,040 --> 00:06:35,170
What happened today

118
00:06:35,390 --> 00:06:37,040
may have looked like it was aimed at me,

119
00:06:37,040 --> 00:06:39,640
but it was actually
Cao Huaitai targeting you.

120
00:06:39,750 --> 00:06:40,580
Yes.

121
00:06:41,560 --> 00:06:43,690
Why does he keep giving you a hard time?

122
00:06:47,630 --> 00:06:48,680
My mother

123
00:06:49,070 --> 00:06:51,270
was essentially killed by Cao Huaitai.

124
00:06:53,890 --> 00:06:55,040
When I was young,

125
00:06:55,060 --> 00:06:56,680
his son, Cao Lingxiu,

126
00:06:56,680 --> 00:06:58,270
used to bully others at the academy.

127
00:06:58,270 --> 00:06:59,480
I couldn't stand it

128
00:06:59,480 --> 00:07:00,940
and fought him.

129
00:07:01,160 --> 00:07:03,890
Cao Huaitai stormed into our
residence with men.

130
00:07:04,560 --> 00:07:06,490
My mother was pushed by Cao Huaitai

131
00:07:07,150 --> 00:07:08,510
and hit her head

132
00:07:09,510 --> 00:07:10,880
while protecting me.

133
00:07:13,240 --> 00:07:14,310
She passed away

134
00:07:15,630 --> 00:07:16,630
not long after.

135
00:07:18,510 --> 00:07:19,920
How outrageous!

136
00:07:20,510 --> 00:07:21,970
What happened after that?

137
00:07:22,500 --> 00:07:24,430
He spent only half a year in prison.

138
00:07:25,920 --> 00:07:28,000
Then he was released.

139
00:07:39,590 --> 00:07:40,710
Cao Huaitai

140
00:07:40,920 --> 00:07:43,870
is a coward who hides behind violence.

141
00:07:45,000 --> 00:07:46,390
You and your mother

142
00:07:46,610 --> 00:07:48,610
are the truly brave ones.

143
00:07:49,190 --> 00:07:50,260
Qiguang,

144
00:07:50,630 --> 00:07:51,510
stop blaming yourself

145
00:07:51,510 --> 00:07:53,280
for it.

146
00:08:16,830 --> 00:08:17,830
Today

147
00:08:18,690 --> 00:08:20,620
is Qinglian's death anniversary.

148
00:08:22,570 --> 00:08:24,090
I made you a new outfit.

149
00:08:25,310 --> 00:08:26,240
Would you

150
00:08:26,400 --> 00:08:27,200
wear it

151
00:08:27,580 --> 00:08:28,540
today?

152
00:08:32,159 --> 00:08:33,039
Would you

153
00:08:33,059 --> 00:08:34,510
wear it

154
00:08:34,600 --> 00:08:35,340
today...

155
00:08:41,270 --> 00:08:42,330
Thank you, Honey.

156
00:08:42,820 --> 00:08:44,350
It's not convenient today.

157
00:08:45,870 --> 00:08:48,200
Please change into plain clothes instead

158
00:08:48,250 --> 00:08:49,890
and join me in the memorial.

159
00:09:00,680 --> 00:09:02,610
I didn't attend before,

160
00:09:03,010 --> 00:09:04,130
and I

161
00:09:04,240 --> 00:09:05,480
won't today either.

162
00:09:07,210 --> 00:09:08,720
My Qinglian

163
00:09:09,050 --> 00:09:10,180
is not dead!

164
00:09:12,690 --> 00:09:14,040
He can't come back.

165
00:09:16,180 --> 00:09:17,330
You know that.

166
00:09:21,100 --> 00:09:22,380
Mo Junyu!

167
00:09:24,210 --> 00:09:27,780
[Qingxin Cottage]

168
00:09:38,360 --> 00:09:39,840
I'm here to pick up Master and Senior

169
00:09:39,840 --> 00:09:41,700
for the trip to the Cicada Agency.

170
00:09:41,940 --> 00:09:43,430
I've been studying the account books

171
00:09:43,430 --> 00:09:44,430
my father left me.

172
00:09:44,960 --> 00:09:46,200
The first and fifteenth of each month

173
00:09:46,200 --> 00:09:47,890
are bookkeeping days.

174
00:09:48,010 --> 00:09:49,760
Master will be busy today.

175
00:09:51,950 --> 00:09:52,750
Master, Senior,

176
00:09:52,750 --> 00:09:53,880
get in the carriage.

177
00:09:54,430 --> 00:09:56,120
Qiguang, you're so thoughtful.

178
00:09:56,120 --> 00:09:57,840
No need to use lightness
skills to fly now.

179
00:09:57,840 --> 00:09:59,440
The carriage is much better.

180
00:10:01,960 --> 00:10:02,630
Master,

181
00:10:02,630 --> 00:10:03,430
come quickly!

182
00:10:12,840 --> 00:10:14,240
Wait until after sunset.

183
00:10:14,320 --> 00:10:15,980
I'll come to take Master home.

184
00:10:17,080 --> 00:10:17,870
Alright.

185
00:10:35,920 --> 00:10:37,250
Is there anything else?

186
00:10:37,260 --> 00:10:39,200
Master will be exhausted!

187
00:10:39,260 --> 00:10:40,480
If you can't sit still,

188
00:10:40,480 --> 00:10:41,940
you can go play for a while.

189
00:10:43,270 --> 00:10:44,390
That's not good, is it?

190
00:10:44,390 --> 00:10:45,460
Master.

191
00:10:48,200 --> 00:10:49,440
Thank you, Master.

192
00:10:57,860 --> 00:10:58,610
Ms. Mo,

193
00:10:58,850 --> 00:11:00,790
there was movement at the
Grand Commandant's Mansion two days ago.

194
00:11:00,790 --> 00:11:02,150
Someone from the Imperial Prison

195
00:11:02,150 --> 00:11:03,390
delivered a letter to Mo Junyu.

196
00:11:03,390 --> 00:11:05,400
[Grand Commandant's Mansion]

197
00:11:04,120 --> 00:11:05,360
It was a letter from Chen Siqi

198
00:11:05,360 --> 00:11:06,840
to the Grand Commandant.

199
00:11:07,930 --> 00:11:09,590
[Imperial Prison]

200
00:11:07,960 --> 00:11:09,320
This morning,

201
00:11:09,320 --> 00:11:11,270
Chen Siqi was released.

202
00:11:15,360 --> 00:11:17,240
It seems that he served well

203
00:11:17,240 --> 00:11:18,320
as a touchstone.

204
00:11:19,030 --> 00:11:19,940
But

205
00:11:20,030 --> 00:11:21,480
it's quite surprising that

206
00:11:21,480 --> 00:11:23,200
he's so deeply connected to

207
00:11:23,480 --> 00:11:25,030
Mo Junyu.

208
00:11:27,750 --> 00:11:28,240
Ms...

209
00:11:28,720 --> 00:11:29,320
Ms. Mo,

210
00:11:29,510 --> 00:11:30,440
are you alright?

211
00:11:31,440 --> 00:11:32,000
I'm fine.

212
00:11:32,080 --> 00:11:32,860
Go on.

213
00:11:33,670 --> 00:11:34,100
Okay.

214
00:11:34,870 --> 00:11:36,330
News from Chu has arrived.

215
00:11:36,630 --> 00:11:37,390
It's highly likely that Feng Shiye

216
00:11:37,390 --> 00:11:39,280
will lead the Chu delegation

217
00:11:39,390 --> 00:11:41,120
to the capital for peace talks.

218
00:11:44,720 --> 00:11:46,570
Mo Qingchuan.

219
00:11:49,800 --> 00:11:50,620
Qi Yun,

220
00:11:51,370 --> 00:11:53,480
activate the Silver Cicada to
send a message.

221
00:11:53,480 --> 00:11:54,760
Dispatch Golden Cicada Zhou

222
00:11:54,760 --> 00:11:56,000
to Chu to investigate

223
00:11:57,480 --> 00:11:59,210
their military deployment.

224
00:11:59,600 --> 00:12:00,440
Okay.

225
00:12:21,570 --> 00:12:25,270
[Vanguard Camp]

226
00:12:23,600 --> 00:12:24,600
Is this

227
00:12:25,750 --> 00:12:28,350
the badge of the Mo Army's
Vanguard Battalion?

228
00:12:29,960 --> 00:12:31,120
Shuicao?

229
00:12:31,840 --> 00:12:34,080
If there really was such a
person in the Vanguard,

230
00:12:34,080 --> 00:12:35,340
there must be a record.

231
00:12:50,150 --> 00:12:52,350
There's really someone named Shuicao.

232
00:13:01,680 --> 00:13:02,650
[Black]

233
00:13:06,840 --> 00:13:08,170
Greetings, Inspector.

234
00:13:08,390 --> 00:13:09,990
Greetings to the four of you.

235
00:13:10,750 --> 00:13:12,310
I may be a bit presumptuous

236
00:13:12,340 --> 00:13:13,740
in seeking you out today,

237
00:13:14,100 --> 00:13:15,060
but I

238
00:13:15,360 --> 00:13:17,090
wish to inquire about someone.

239
00:13:17,690 --> 00:13:18,850
Please ask.

240
00:13:19,150 --> 00:13:20,480
I'll tell you all I know.

241
00:13:21,600 --> 00:13:22,440
Sir, since you

242
00:13:22,570 --> 00:13:24,700
once served under General Qingchuan,

243
00:13:24,730 --> 00:13:26,360
may I ask if you

244
00:13:26,770 --> 00:13:28,100
knew someone

245
00:13:28,740 --> 00:13:29,600
named Shuicao?

246
00:13:40,860 --> 00:13:41,410
Sir.

247
00:13:43,440 --> 00:13:44,500
Why do you

248
00:13:44,630 --> 00:13:45,910
ask about this?

249
00:13:47,880 --> 00:13:49,040
I happened to hear the name

250
00:13:49,040 --> 00:13:50,880
in passing recently

251
00:13:50,960 --> 00:13:52,000
and grew curious.

252
00:13:52,290 --> 00:13:53,490
Please rest assured,

253
00:13:53,670 --> 00:13:54,720
I mean no harm.

254
00:13:55,840 --> 00:13:57,240
Shuicao?

255
00:13:58,240 --> 00:13:59,550
Wasn't she standing right next to you

256
00:13:59,550 --> 00:14:01,610
during the martial arts tournament?

257
00:14:05,880 --> 00:14:06,890
I see.

258
00:14:07,120 --> 00:14:09,000
She was General Qingchuan's shadow guard,

259
00:14:09,000 --> 00:14:09,670
but

260
00:14:09,670 --> 00:14:11,450
due to her special status,

261
00:14:11,590 --> 00:14:12,310
I'm afraid

262
00:14:13,370 --> 00:14:14,310
I can't

263
00:14:14,340 --> 00:14:15,650
reveal more.

264
00:14:16,660 --> 00:14:18,880
So Master's really Shuicao.

265
00:14:23,030 --> 00:14:23,910
It's alright.

266
00:14:24,590 --> 00:14:25,980
You have all remained loyal

267
00:14:25,980 --> 00:14:26,960
and fearless in the face of power.

268
00:14:26,960 --> 00:14:27,630
I

269
00:14:27,630 --> 00:14:29,080
will remember this.

270
00:14:40,370 --> 00:14:41,560
If he comes asking,

271
00:14:40,970 --> 00:14:43,260
[Order]

272
00:14:41,590 --> 00:14:42,510
just say that.

273
00:14:42,530 --> 00:14:43,590
Do you understand?

274
00:14:44,200 --> 00:14:44,670
Yes.

275
00:14:44,890 --> 00:14:45,990
I know.

276
00:14:51,870 --> 00:14:53,260
Master once said

277
00:14:53,280 --> 00:14:54,240
the Mo Army

278
00:14:54,270 --> 00:14:55,730
would rise again.

279
00:14:57,390 --> 00:14:58,240
Alright.

280
00:14:58,710 --> 00:15:00,840
We'll wait for the Young General's return.

281
00:15:00,840 --> 00:15:01,630
Okay.

282
00:15:06,570 --> 00:15:09,920
[Qingxin Cottage]

283
00:15:10,630 --> 00:15:11,120
Eat up,

284
00:15:11,120 --> 00:15:12,020
Shuicao.

285
00:15:14,330 --> 00:15:16,130
He's such a fickle guy, isn't he?

286
00:15:18,360 --> 00:15:20,460
So just because I'm not Mo Qingchuan,

287
00:15:20,750 --> 00:15:22,200
you stop calling me Master?

288
00:15:22,200 --> 00:15:23,420
Exactly.

289
00:15:29,270 --> 00:15:30,990
Why didn't you tell me earlier

290
00:15:31,020 --> 00:15:32,220
that you are Shuicao?

291
00:15:34,600 --> 00:15:37,340
What is there to be proud of about

292
00:15:37,750 --> 00:15:40,440
being the shadow guard of
the traitor, Mo Qingchuan?

293
00:15:40,440 --> 00:15:42,440
Mo Qingchuan is not a traitor!

294
00:15:56,750 --> 00:15:57,480
Master,

295
00:15:57,480 --> 00:15:58,630
