443
00:22:10,960 --> 00:22:12,400
Why did you betray me?

444
00:22:12,700 --> 00:22:14,520
Why did you betray the Mo Army?

445
00:22:16,240 --> 00:22:17,310
Back then,

446
00:22:17,750 --> 00:22:19,540
I was sent by you

447
00:22:19,570 --> 00:22:21,330
to investigate Liya Town

448
00:22:21,580 --> 00:22:22,580
but

449
00:22:23,010 --> 00:22:24,690
